			            </a>

						<a href="flota.html" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border-t-4 border-indigo-500">
						                <div class="text-indigo-600 text-4xl mb-3">🚚</div>
